# ⭐ Features of Java

## 1. Simple

Java has a simple syntax that is easy to learn and understand.

```java
public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        System.out.println("Hello, Java!");
    }
}
```

---

## 2. Object-Oriented

Java follows Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) concepts:

* Class
* Object
* Inheritance
* Polymorphism
* Abstraction
* Encapsulation

---

## 3. Platform Independent

Java code is compiled into **Bytecode**, which can run on any operating system using JVM.

```text
Java Code
    ↓
Compiler
    ↓
Bytecode (.class)
    ↓
JVM
    ↓
Windows / Linux / macOS
```

---

## 4. Secure

Java provides several security features:

* No explicit pointers
* Bytecode verification
* Security Manager
* Runtime checking

---

## 5. Robust

Java provides:

* Exception Handling
* Automatic Memory Management
* Garbage Collection

---

## 6. Multithreaded

Java supports multiple threads, allowing programs to perform several tasks simultaneously.

Example:

* Downloading a file
* Playing music
* Updating the UI

All at the same time.

---

## 7. High Performance

Java uses the **Just-In-Time (JIT) Compiler** to improve execution speed.

---

## 8. Distributed

Java can create distributed applications that work across multiple systems over a network.

---

# 🏗 Java Architecture

```text
Java Source Code (.java)
            │
            ▼
     Java Compiler (javac)
            │
            ▼
      Bytecode (.class)
            │
            ▼
     Java Virtual Machine
            │
            ▼
Operating System
(Windows/Linux/macOS)
```

---

# ☕ Components of Java

## JVM (Java Virtual Machine)

* Executes Java Bytecode
* Platform dependent

## JRE (Java Runtime Environment)

Contains:

* JVM
* Java Libraries
* Supporting Files

Used to run Java applications.

## JDK (Java Development Kit)

Contains:

* JRE
* JVM
* Java Compiler
* Debugger
* Development Tools

Used to develop Java applications.

---

# 📊 JDK vs JRE vs JVM

| Feature            | JVM | JRE | JDK |
| ------------------ | --- | --- | --- |
| Runs Java Programs | ✅   | ✅   | ✅   |
| JVM Included       | ❌   | ✅   | ✅   |
| Compiler Included  | ❌   | ❌   | ✅   |
| Development Tools  | ❌   | ❌   | ✅   |

